## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="eab02-104">方法必須為 static 和 public。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eab02-104">The method must be static and public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="eab02-105">它必須傳回所有 WMI 類別執行個體的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eab02-105">It must return a collection of all instances of the WMI class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="eab02-106">集合可以是任何類型可轉換為<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eab02-106">The collection can be of any type convertible to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="eab02-107">下列範例會示範如何使用列舉值屬性來標記方法，用來列舉類別的執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eab02-107">The following example shows how to use the Enumerator attribute to mark a method that is used to enumerate instances of a class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="eab02-108">在此情況下，會使用列舉方法<xref:System.Diagnostics.Process>類別來擷取所有電腦上執行的處理序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eab02-108">In this case, the Enumerate method uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process> class to retrieve all of the processes running on the computer.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[ManagementEnumerator]  
public static IEnumerable Enumerate()  
{  
   Process[] rgProcesses = Process.GetProcesses();  
   for (int i = 0; i < rgProcesses.Length; i++)  
   {  
      yield return new ProcessProvider(rgProcesses[i]);  
   }  
}  
```
